    "Reduces the probability of generating nonsense. A higher value (e.g. 100) will give more diverse answers, while a lower value (e.g. 10) will be more conservative": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Reduces the probability of generating nonsense. A higher value (e.g. 100) will give more diverse answers, while a lower value (e.g. 10) will be more conservative"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Réduit la probabilité de générer des absurdités. Une valeur plus élevée (ex. 100) donnera des réponses plus diverses, tandis qu'une valeur plus basse (ex. 10) sera plus conservatrice"
          }
        }
      }
